title: #92Noon! Randy Sampson/Adam Caplan/Michael Russo/Kydra De St Aubin/Matt Birk
description: Canterbury Park President, Randy Sampson, starts the show off with PA going over how business has changed since COVID-19.  Adam Caplan calls in to talk NFL.  Michael Russo discusses the NHL bubble situation.  MN United Commentator. Kyndra De St Aubin, breaks down the return of MLS.  And finally, Matt Birk joins the show for his weekly segment to talk some more NFL.
